<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              xmlns:local="clr-namespace:mahjongNEA"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="14" FontFamily="Georgia">
    <Paragraph FontSize="18">
        <Bold FontSize="22">Heavenly Hand:</Bold>
        <LineBreak/>
        The dealer wins with the initial hand.
        <LineBreak/>
        <LineBreak/>
        <Bold FontSize="22">Earthly Hand:</Bold>
        <LineBreak/>
        Non dealer players win with the dealer's first discard.
        <LineBreak/>
        <LineBreak/>
        <Bold FontSize="22">Thirteen Orphans:</Bold>
        <LineBreak/>
        The complete hand contains one of all terminal or honour tiles, with one of them repeating.
        <LineBreak/>
        e.g.:
        <LineBreak/>
        <InlineUIContainer>
            <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="1m.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="9m.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="1s.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="9s.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="1p.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="9p.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="2z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="3z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="4z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="5z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="6z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="7z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="8z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="8z.jpg"/>
            </StackPanel>
        </InlineUIContainer>
        <LineBreak/>
        <LineBreak/>
        <Bold FontSize="22">Great Winds:</Bold>
        <LineBreak/>
        The complete hand contains all 4 winds as melds
        <LineBreak/>
        e.g.:
        <LineBreak/>
        <InlineUIContainer>
            <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="2z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="2z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="2z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="3z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="3z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="3z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="4z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="4z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="4z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="5z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="5z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="5z.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="1p.jpg"/>
                <Image Margin="0,0,0,2" Source="1p.jpg"/>
            </StackPanel>
        </InlineUIContainer>
        <LineBreak/>
        <LineBreak/>
        <Bold FontSize="22">All Kongs:</Bold>
        <LineBreak/>
        The winning hand has 4 kongs and an eye.
        <LineBreak/>
        <LineBreak/>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>
